parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoEx.Nellie left before the demons came out of the rift. She hasn’t returned!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.A demon named Daemalius took Erica and he’s looking to take revenge on Madalyn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoEx.Madalyn tricked him and used him to open the rift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Did you see Lilith? Did the demons have the Toma with them?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaEx^.Negative. Only demons and no statue to be seen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoCl.I have no idea where Lillian is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ObWoCl.Not exactly the highest priority right now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.We lost her… This new demon named Daemalius took her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx^.We have to open the rift and bomb the shit out of it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx^.We lost Erica and we have a bomb. It’s worth a shot.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoDe^.It could work… All of the worlds are vulnerable to attack.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Daemalius wants revenge. He’ll come here. I know it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx^.Find hairs from Lillian or any other demon part…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe^.If this new monster comes here, what the hell are we supposed to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx^.We have an arsenal of holy weapons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx^.I can help. I can help protect everyone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Father can handle demons. I’ve seen it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.Are you going to open the rift?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.Why are you here? Who’s keeping an eye on the girls?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx^.They are safe in the church. Stay focused.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ll search the mansion for Nellie… and see if I can find more demon parts to open the rift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoEx.Erica’s soul could be waiting for us on the other side.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Father… Stay here and make sure everyone is safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoEx.Hurry and open the rift. We have to save Erica… And find the Toma.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErMaAgNo1^.You’ve chosen the wrong place to run. Do you dare bring me to Hell?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFlDe.What better place to end this feud?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Uhh… That could be a problem… The girls are in Hell too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErMaAg^.You can’t run anymore. It’s time to make this right.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Stay low so they don’t see us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I have no idea… But it’s a popular hangout spot for those creepy sick guys.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.This is some sort of torture chamber.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.Us, if we don’t get out of here soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I don’t think that’s what it is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There is something on the other side of that strange metal thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.As long as those lepers are around there’s no way to get through.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.So… What are you going to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Come on. Let’s get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.You don’t have to ask me twice.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnCl.Ouch! What the hell was that all about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlEx^.We beat her at her own game.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlOp.You won that battle. But you’ve lost the war.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.One step ahead. Henry is already on the way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Those women… What did they do to me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.Relax, 1Hero. You’ve only been given a taste.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.What type of portal is this? Where does it go?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.The rift has been opened to a world in need and I am here to save it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.Oh, but it is and soon peace shall be restored.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoBaOp.Mother, what shall we do with him?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.I believe our friend here has work tomorrow…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlDe.We better let him get a good night’s rest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnOp.We will let him leave the mansion!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.There are officers outside… If I go missing…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.Of course you can leave, 1Hero. Why would I break my trust with you now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.You are a man of honor, 1Hero, are you not?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.Complete the Toma Leolo so I can save the fallen realm.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.What are you going to do, Lillian? Tell me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.I am here to collect the Toma Leolo… With it, I can grant new life to the damned…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.I can return peace and harmony to all realms.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’ve been visited by an angel. I also saw those demons in my dream.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx.The Empyrean knows no suffering. There is no concern for anyone in the realms of chaos and misery…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.It is my mission alone to save them. Will you help me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Those demon women… They need our help?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Where are the rest of the Toma pieces?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.They are here in North Santiva, 1Hero… It is up to you to find them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.You are forbidden from entering the rift. Go back to the surface.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.Do not question it, 1Hero. I know what’s best.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnDe.Step away from the rift. You are not allowed back in without Mother.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How do you activate the rift?... I don’t see anything back here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How do you activate the rift?... I don’t see anything back here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How do you activate the rift?... I don’t see anything back here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How do you activate the rift?... I don’t see anything back here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How do you activate the rift?... I don’t see anything back here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.We can’t just go in there! It’s dangerous.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdWoCl.Jesus Christ… She had me in her grasp… How did she do it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Where were you? Why did you come here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.I came here to handle Duncan myself. What the hell are you doing here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Kimberly spotted you and called me. She’s looking to deepen the Guild story.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Because it’s not that simple, 1Hero. You don’t need to know everything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I can handle it. I want to know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.We need control. We can’t have a power vacuum filled by a crazy person…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.So you’re just letting the Guild survive?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Don’t be so dramatic. This isn’t unusual.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.We’re using a criminal organization to funnel low-lifes into our grasp. It’s a trap as old as the legal system itself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.But what about people getting hurt or killed? What about all the art theft?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Don’t pretend you care more about art than me. This is for the greater good.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.So some people have to suffer for the benefit of the many?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.It’s either that, or we kill him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Nellie killed Charles under my command. The Guild has been falling under my orders.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.Duncan is the last piece that I chose to leave standing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.We could kill him and see what pops up in his place. But I’d rather avoid that. Wouldn’t you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.The thieves come to Duncan, and I choose who we chase.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.That means not everyone will be put away. We can’t make it obvious.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Oh, God. This isn’t what I wanted to hear.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Be a detective, 1Hero. It’s what you’re good at.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.And give up all that I worked so hard to set up?... I think not.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Now, how the hell do we get out of here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I just need some items. I’ll only be a moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.Thank God I’m a priest, or I’d be pissing my pants right about now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe.I’m bored. When are we going to kick some demon ass?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrMaAg.I have a crucifix! You better get back!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiMaEx^.You’re standing in my way! You will not take him from us!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.It’s okay, Brian. I made peace with them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx^.You are the one brainwashing the people of Earth!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiMaAgNo1^.These worlds are governed by chaos. And it’s people like you that have let it happen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnOp^.It’s time, 1Hero. You know what to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.Tasha ran with her to the church… I came back after I didn’t see you following us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.We need to get back to the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I don’t know where they went… They can fend for themselves.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.We saved Kimberly from the monsters… That’s good enough for now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "GnWoCl.Is it supposed to glow like that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFlOp^.Divert your gaze if you value your soul.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFlEx^.You will be the first soldiers in a war between worlds.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFlEx^.Come. It’s time to give you purpose.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.They went through the rift… They went to Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnDe.Damn… Looks like it’s not open anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx.They are dead. Your goons are dead.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Take Miss Foxx and the maid away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.You really want to get your men back?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I know how to do it… I think.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Go to Eve Cathedral and get Zephaniah’s journal…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Once we open the rift, I will face Madalyn and we will steal back the Toma Leolo.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.No… The men are gone. Get the Toma.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnDe^.Artifact hunting in a moment like this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I trust the priest. He says they are dead.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx.Their souls have been sent to judgment. Their bodies will be used as vessels for monsters.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnDe^.Who cares? I just need bodies. Find my men.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Give me some time. I’ll find them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Daemalius is blocking us from leaving! I have to go through the rift!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.It’s a battle! They are fighting each other!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoWoOp>.What the fuck do we do now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnEx.We go to Hell and we bring the bomb with us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoOp^.How are we going to save Erica now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Lillian said her soul will appear on the altar in Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrEx.She’ll do it! I believe in her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnEx^.Everyone, stop your bickering and let’s get our asses to Hell!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.I can’t follow… But I will do what I can from here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.Be useful and get my men back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaOp.We’ll take care of anything that comes through that portal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.You’re really good at handling that katana.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlDe.Almost as good as I am at handling a cock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.1Hero, Henry here says you heard the name Lilith.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.It’s what Lillian said… But she didn’t look like herself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoDe.Lilith is a demon from Hell, but she shouldn’t exist.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.What are you talking about? She called herself Lilith.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Lilith is Jewish folklore and, as we all know, Catholicism is the one true religion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.I think you picked the wrong religion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlDe.Ah… But may I remind you that my powers worked on those demons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I’m telling you, it’s Lilith… But she had bigger boobs than she had as Lillian… and a demon-like face.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.That’s very strange… If she’s a demon, how does she leave through the portal?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.Never heard of a human form… Maybe she’s a demi-demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoOp^.I wish I could tell you I know how to stop her… but I can’t come up with any ideas.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Father, take Zephaniah’s journal… Maybe there’s something in it you can use.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I think I know where they are going.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Kimberly is going to try and broadcast the Toma on TV… But Paul won’t let her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnOp.And that’s why she has a posse of demons: to take the studio by force.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.Madalyn and Lillian are still on the other side of the rift…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.But, Father, we have to stop the broadcast.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElBaEx^.Go to the Channel 4 building. I’ll take care of the demon women.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoWoEx.I can’t believe I’m saying this, but I’m glad a priest is here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Good luck, 1Hero. I have no idea how you plan to open this weird portal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Bring me Zephaniah’s journal. It should be in the cathedral library.");
//////// If MC hasn't found the girls yet ////////
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Give me the journal and go back and make sure they are safe. This could take a while.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I’ll find them and make sure they are safe.");
//////// If MC has found the girls ////////
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.The usual place… Into a puff of black smoke.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx.Take the journal and see what you can figure out. I’m going back to the church to find Sister Judy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.What’s the deal? Why isn’t the rift open?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’m working on it. Give me some time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx^.I’m with the sexy cop. You need to move faster.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.Diana is surprisingly knowledgeable about the Casula.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.But hopefully Henry comes back with something helpful.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx>.Just go inside and take a peek.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx>.Go in there, Vayne. You’re a woman. She’ll go easy on you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.What the hell? She was out here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.She didn’t go through the rift with me… I don’t think.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnOp.Tell them! They don’t know the plan!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.Is he arrested or not? We’re not leaving here until we know he’s done.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.Do we need to go back to Hell for another rescue mission?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Madalyn has the Toma. What can we do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.We’re not exactly sure how to control it… But maybe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.Tasha was right. Things are getting out of control.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoCl^.Oh, no. How do we get back inside?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlOp.You really think your commissioner went through that glowing door?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I didn’t see any of Duncan’s henchmen inside the rift… But it’s safe to assume they are possessed monsters at this point.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaDe^.I know a thing or two about demons… If there’s a way to close that portal for good, I think I can figure it out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrFlEx^.Trust me. I know a thing or two about magic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.I was able to open it. Maybe I can help you close it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx^.I hate to throw a wrench into your system… But Duncan isn’t the only criminal in this room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnExNo1.Diana is Guild! Morgan is Guild! Nellie is Guild!... Hell… Canmore is my damned son. He killed a man no more than an hour ago. You’re all fucked!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.He’s trying to confuse us… Take him to jail.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.Check his gun! The body is buried out front in a shallow grave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlDe.No… No one’s going to jail this evening. Unless you take all of us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Duncan’s goon… Victor, or whatever his name was… He tried to shoot Ella.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.You put a bullet in his brain…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlDe.And Morgan… You giving up your millions? I think not.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Okay… Listen up… None of us leaves the mansion until we figure out what the hell is going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.Then we’re putting a bullet in Duncan’s head.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Father Solomon… Work with Henry and figure out a way to keep this portal from reopening.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Ella, Diana… Stay here and don’t let the Toma Leolo leave Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Only a human can pass through that rift… If it’s not Kimberly… Kill it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I’m not leaving the portal. If it opens, I need to be ready.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErSaEx^.I can help, too. It was my fault.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrSaEx.Let’s not go assigning blame. Madalyn manipulated you…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx^.The Toma Leolo is a Casula artifact. Maybe there is more to learn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Go find Tasha and Nellie… They can help you learn more at the church library.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaOp^.I’ll go to the porn shop… I’ll let Tasha know the plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlDe.I happen to be something of an expert on Casula culture as well.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlEx.I’ve stolen a lot of Casula artifacts in my time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Maybe you and I can compare notes then.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.It’s settled, then. We’re going to figure this out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeSaDe^.I guess this might just be the end of the road for my career.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnOp.You’re all going to pay for this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnOp^.Ready to get shot in the head, Duncan?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnOp.Want me to stab you in the chest again, miracle boy?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Lock Helmer in the west office upstairs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe.Who’s going to make sure he doesn’t escape?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe.I guess we’re with you, Father Solomon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrEx^.Don’t worry. Between the three of us, we can handle anything that steps outside that portal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "You can now find this character profile in your album.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Are you keeping an eye on the rift?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ObWoCl.That girl in the armor is freaking me out. Why is she wearing armor!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFrEx.If I see anything, I’ll give you a call.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.What are you girls doing down here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoOp^.How the hell do we open the rift?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.If we can stop Lilith and close the rift, they can keep the damn Toma.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoEx^.How can you say that? They could find a way to use it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.You really think you can enter Hell and find a magic rock that, if you look at it, you’ll die?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrEx^.If anyone can do it, I can.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnEx^.Fine. But we’ll have to deal with this rift eventually.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Be careful, Ella. Finding the Toma isn’t worth losing your life.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Just keep an eye on the rift and let me know if you see anything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaWoCl.This is all crazy. This has to be a trick.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaEx.Find my mom. We could use her help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.Are you going to open the rift?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I know you want to do what’s right, 1Hero… The world is at stake.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I’ll find a way to open the rift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.Don’t worry, 1Hero… Erica’s soul will be okay. One way or another.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.I came here to kill Duncan and now we’re dealing with demons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrFrEx.I’m here for a reason, 1Hero… I believe we’ll succeed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe.I wonder if there’s a clear path to the surface.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.No! Let me go… I’ll make sure he gets out.");
